ocal.com/2020/01/14/enthusiastic-crowd-lines-up-hours-ahead-of-time-for-president-trumps-rally-in-milwaukee/ \"Enthusiastic Crowd Gathers For President Trump\u2019s Rally In Milwaukee\"], CBS Chicago/CBS News/[[WBBM-TV|CBS 2]], January 14, 2020.</ref>\n|-\n|-\n|Tuesday, January 28, 2020\n|[[Wildwood, New Jersey|Wildwood]]\n|[[New Jersey|NJ]]\n|[[Wildwoods Convention Center]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|-\n|Thursday, January 30, 2020\n|[[Des Moines, Iowa|Des Moines]]\n|[[Iowa|IA]]\n|[[Knapp Center]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|-\n|Monday, February 10, 2020\n|[[Manchester, New Hampshire|Manchester]]\n|[[New Hampshire|NH]]\n|[[SNHU Arena]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|-\n| Wednesday, February 19, 2020\n| [[Phoenix, Arizona|Phoenix]]\n| [[Arizona|AZ]]\n| [[Arizona Veterans Memorial Coliseum]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|-\n| Thursday, February 20, 2020\n| [[Colorado Springs, Colorado|Colorado Springs]]\n| [[Colorado|CO]]\n| [[Broadmoor World Arena (1998)|Broadmoor World Arena]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|-\n| Friday, February 21, 2020\n| [[Las Vegas, Nevada|Las Vegas]]\n| [[Nevada|NV]]\n| [[Las Vegas Convention Center]]\n| \n|\n|-\n|-\n| Friday, February 28, 2020\n| [[North Charleston, South Carolina|North Charleston]]\n| [[South Carolina|SC]]\n| [[North Charleston Coliseum|North Charleston Coliseum & Performing Arts Center]]\n| \n| \n|-\n|-\n| Monday, March 2, 2020\n| [[Charlotte, North Carolina|Charlotte]]\n| [[North Carolina|NC]]\n| [[Bojangles' Coliseum]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n==Political positions==\n{{Main|Political positions of Donald Trump}}\n\n==See also==\n{{Wikipedia books|Campaigns of Donald Trump}}\n* [[Donald Trump 2000 presidential campaign]]\n* [[Donald Trump 2016 presidential campaign]]\n* [[Facebook\u2013Cambridge Analytica data scandal]]\n* [[List of Donald Trump 2020 presidential campaign endorsements]]\n* [[Opinion polling on the Donald Trump administration]]\n* [[Political positions of Donald Trump]]\n* [[Presidency of Donald Trump]]\n* [[2020 Republican Party presidential primaries]]\n\n==Notes==\n{{Reflist|group=note}}\n\n==Refer